{"type":"message","id":"c6458fbe","parentId":"a1c3610a","timestamp":"2026-04-22T04:49:48.080Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-04-22 04:49 UTC] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: Analyze the AHVTEACHER project at /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be and create detailed Confluence documentation.\n\n1. Read all model files in src/infrastructure/database/models/\n2. Read all route files in src/interface/routes/\n3. Read all service files in src/application/services/\n4. Read README.md and any existing docs/\n\nThen create detailed documentation pages in Confluence space AHVTEACHER with this structure (matching OTLXPA1):\n\nUse this API to create pages:\n```bash\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://dtlx.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content\" \\\n  -u \"ninhkhuongpl7@gmail.com:ATATT3xFfGF0bFjmIN6IPHwDzRChO8oMe5XAaA6dheluE8J2eUTNZHLgprik7oLx-vNnZsNVCb4cAAjziLDb27lKFHU2_RTgdeuv8zMkaPR-or2gSJQjHp8TMmOtI53F6MauTeaXX5Tg4gdMYyJ2nUKI-2HSMvK4TLkXLmKSKrdGrOpNDLRgMxA=8865492F\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"type\":\"page\",\"title\":\"PAGE_TITLE\",\"space\":{\"key\":\"AHVTEACHER\"},\"body\":{\"storage\":{\"value\":\"HTML_CONTENT\",\"representation\":\"storage\"}}}'\n```\n\nCreate these pages with detailed content (HTML format):\n\n1. \"0. TỔNG QUAN\" - Project overview, tech stack, architecture diagram\n2. \"1. QUẢN LÝ NGƯỜI DÙNG\" - User management (User model, roles, CRUD endpoints)\n3. \"2. QUẢN LÝ KHÓA HỌC\" - Course management (Course model, lessons, enrollment)\n4. \"3. QUẢN LÝ HỌC VIÊN\" - Student management (Student model, enrollment, progress)\n5. \"4. QUẢN LÝ GIÁO VIÊN\" - Teacher management\n6. \"5. LỊCH THI\" - Exam schedules (Exam model, schedule management)\n7. \"6. QUẢN LÝ SÂN THI\" - Stadium management\n8. \"7. THANH TOÁN\" - Payment management\n9. \"8. BÁO CÁO\" - Dashboard and reporting\n10. \"9. THÔNG BÁO\" - Notification system\n11. \"10. HỖ TRỢ\" - Support request system\n\nEach page should include:\n- Mục đích (Purpose)\n- Cấu trúc dữ liệu (Data structure) - field names, types, enums\n- API Endpoints (method, path, params, response)\n- Ví dụ (Examples)\n- Luồng xử lý (Flow)\n\nUse HTML formatting for tables, lists, code blocks."}],"timestamp":1776833388047}}
